From 0000000000000000000000000000000000000000 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: sarun <noreply@sarun>
Date: Sun, 19 Jul 2026 20:04:46 +0000
Subject: [PATCH] find: defer reference metadata through matcher context

Parse -newer, file-backed -newerXY, and -samefile into typed reference queries without touching the filesystem. Resolve every matcher-tree branch through the read-only FindContext before consuming files0 inputs or preparing output actions. This also fixes logical-cwd and symlink-following behavior, implements candidate X versus reference Y exactly, and exposes reference evidence from the execution parser for contextual completion.

---
